317
01:17:24,600 --> 01:17:26,600
Is no one answering?

318
01:17:26,600 --> 01:17:28,600
Hey, anyone home?

319
01:17:30,980 --> 01:17:32,980
Really? By Bacchus!

320
01:17:32,980 --> 01:17:34,980
Hey, anyone home?

321
01:17:35,800 --> 01:17:37,550
Chi è ?
Who is it?

322
01:17:37,560 --> 01:17:42,700
It's me, Filippo. It's Nencio.
Open up, don't you recognize me?

323
01:17:42,700 --> 01:17:44,940
