327
01:17:53,500 --> 01:18:01,000
I've invited the relatives and if you want, the wedding can be held tonight

328
01:18:01,500 --> 01:18:04,000
You can go marry a galley

329
01:18:05,740 --> 01:18:07,740
Rogue, scoundrel,
Accursed rascal!

330
01:18:09,100 --> 01:18:12,400
Go to your wife,
Go feed your children

331
01:18:12,660 --> 01:18:14,000
Unworthy!

332
01:18:14,300 --> 01:18:18,300
Get out of my sight, or taste this rod

333
01:18:32,400 --> 01:18:42,000
You would marry Sandrina?

334
01:18:42,620 --> 01:18:47,720
Get that thought out of your head

335
01:18:47,720 --> 01:19:05,720
Either the gallows or the pillory, perhaps one day, will marry you

336
01:19:07,300 --> 01:19:18,300
Never come before me again, true scum of scoundrels

337
01:19:18,940 --> 01:19:29,160
Full of vices and sins

338
01:19:29,160 --> 01:19:48,120
