339
01:20:28,980 --> 01:20:34,980
You would marry Sandrina?

340
01:20:48,300 --> 01:20:53,100
People are murmering,

341
01:20:53,260 --> 01:21:05,260
The miserable wife begs for mercy

342
01:21:05,260 --> 01:21:13,160
The unfortunate abandoned has no aid,

343
01:21:13,620 --> 01:21:18,000
She has no bread

344
01:21:20,100 --> 01:21:31,100
Never come before me again, true scum of scoundrels

345
01:22:20,420 --> 01:22:43,420
without love, nor charity

346
