V: Ah, is he drunk?
N: Bravo! That's the way to put it

360
01:24:21,080 --> 01:24:23,860
I had recognizing your face

361
01:24:24,940 --> 01:24:26,940
From with me, we go back to the pub?

362
01:24:27,860 --> 01:24:29,860
